Technology - positive developments
    
   -  





Recent years technology has became very widespread in our lives with its advantages and disadvantages.
Some people think that we should pay attention to our lives technology taking control our lives,
while others think that technology makes our lives easy and brings a lot of advantages to world and humanity.

It's clear that technology helps a lot medical domains. We can detect easily the majority of diseases using the IRM or medical scanner. In addition it helps a lot to Pharmaceutical industry.    



 
